---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import aboutImg from '../assets/aboutimg.jpg';
---
<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-[#f8f9f7]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">

        <div class="bg-white rounded-[3.5rem] p-10 md:p-20 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden relative">

            <div class="absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-64 h-64 bg-[#a4b494]/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center relative z-10">

                <div class="relative group">
                    <div class="rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105">
                        <Image 
                        src={aboutImg}
                        alt="About CholoroFy"
                        class="w-full h-125 object-cover"
                        />
                    </div>

                    <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 bg-[#1a1c19] text-white p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-xl">
                        <p class="text-3xl font-black text-[#a4b494]">05+</p>
                        <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400">Years Innovation</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[#4b5d3f] mb-6">Who We Are</h2>
                    <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter text-[#1a1c19] leading-tight mb-8">
                        Dedikasi untuk <br> <span class="text-[#a4b494]">Infrastruktur Berkelanjutan.</span>
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Cholorofy lahir dari keresahan akan dampak industrialisasi terhadap lingkungan. Kami dari tim Strawberry Coding Club 3 percaya bahwa teknologi tidak harus merusak alam.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Melalui riset mendalam. Kami menggabungkan kecerdasan buatan dengan sistem biologis untuk menciptakan kota yang bisa "bernapas" dan menghidupi dirinya sendiri secara mandiri.
                    </p>

                    <div class="space-y-4 mb-10">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#f0f4fc] flex items-center justify-center text-[#4b5d3f]">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[10px]"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-[#1a1c19]">Misi Nol Emisi Karbon</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#f0f4ec] flex items-center justify-center text-[#4b5d3f]">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[10px]"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-[#1a1c19]">Integrasi AI & Biometrik</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <button class="px-10 py-5 bg-[#4b5d3f] text-white rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-[#1a1c19] transition-all hover:shadow-xl shadow-matcha/20">
                        Meet Our Visionary
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>